Apa yang kau lihat?

42
00:06:36.490 --> 00:06:37.540
Aku beri tahu,

43
00:06:39.450 --> 00:06:41.220
jangan berpikir aneh-aneh,

44
00:06:43.130 --> 00:06:43.980
mengerti?

45
00:06:51.060 --> 00:06:52.620
Hanya ada satu kamar utama
di penginapan ini.

46
00:06:53.330 --> 00:06:53.740
Serang.

47
00:07:30.620 --> 00:07:32.180
Aku sudah lama menunggu kalian.

48
