93
00:14:32.210 --> 00:14:33.060
Ayah.

94
00:14:33.690 --> 00:14:35.810
- Letakkan pedangmu!
- Ayah!

95
00:14:36.610 --> 00:14:37.610
Xuan'er,

96
00:14:39.970 --> 00:14:41.330
tutup matamu.

97
00:14:43.330 --> 00:14:43.970
Letakkan!

98
00:14:44.090 --> 00:14:45.690
Jangan, Ayah.

99
00:14:46.330 --> 00:14:47.540
Jangan.

100
00:15:22.780 --> 00:15:23.970
Jangan, Ayah.

101
00:15:24.090 --> 00:15:25.330
Ayah!

102
00:15:34.330 --> 00:15:36.120
- Jalan ke sini.
